T1  - Neither a borrower nor a lender: Does China's zero net foreign asset position make economic sense?
AU  - Dollar, David
AU  - Kraay, Aart
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 53
IS  - 5
SP  - 943
EP  - 971
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/07/01/
